summary: SilverxCristal Commission Info - 2019 DLC Hello there! I’m SilverxCristal and this is my Commission chart, up to date. I’m a...
caption:
SilverxCristal Commission Info - 2019 DLC

Hello there! I’m SilverxCristal and this is my Commission chart, up to date.

I’m a Illustrator student, currently on my 4th and final year, my career requires me to make a lot of manual works, traditional art and print the digital ones. 
I don’t have enough free time to have a part time job and I need to pay my studies and art supplies that are required every week.

I have a Ko-Fi page where I draw something exclusive after every coffee bought but I personally enjoy working on commissions more.

Prices are on top! If you need more examples feel free to check my artblog or ask me without compromises.

Whats new?:

  • Chart with up to date art
  • Updated prices [you wont even see the change] 
  • Added the Icon commissions [15$] events that happen around the year
  • Removed Lineart commissions [15$] due no sales
  • Background [+10] are detailed backgrounds, with a theme. 
  • Tiping will turn into a simple background, depending of the price of the tip
  • Added Twitter as a way to communication

If you are interested:

  • Contact me via tumblr message, twitter message or email; silverxcristal@gmail.com
  • I will need a visual reference of what you want [character desing and colors]. If you have a pose in mind please tell me so I can work with that.
  • You have to pay me before I get started. No refunds!
  • Payment will be done through Paypal, I will show you the invoice one the deposit is done.
  • I’ll try to finish your commission in a week [7 days]. You can ask about how is the process doing and I will give you updates.
  • I will give you the finished commission before I post it on my social media, if you dont want me to post it I will respect that. You are free to post the commission whenever you want! Just remember to credit me.
  • If something goes wrong on the process, I will edit your image up to a max of 3 times.

I will draw:

  • OCs
  • Fanart
  • Shipping
  • Humans
  • Mobians [Sonic characters]
  • F//urries/Anthro
  • FNaF
  • Cookie Run
  • Mechas [Not too detailed]
  • Gijinkas
  • As long there is a reference I can draw that

I won’t draw:

  • Super detailed mechas
  • Realistic people or realistic animals
  • I//nce//st and all variations
  • P//edo//filia and all variations
  • G//or//e
  • Offensive content
  • N//SF//W [P//orn]*
  • S//elf//cest**

If you can’t commission me but want to help, I would apreciate if you share this information so more people can see it. 

Especially now that Tumblr is shadow banning posts with links ajkhlsdjkas

Thank you!

*N//SF//W: I do draw NSFW, however prices are a little different. Contact me if you’re interested in a NSFW commission, no compromises. I will require you to be 18+

**S//elf//cest: I won’t draw direct selfcest, variations of the same character can be conversable.

summary: this is kinda stupid but i wanted to draw space, a night sky, ect. and i wanted to sort of include my precious bb kitty...
caption:
this is kinda stupid but i wanted to draw space, a night sky, ect. and i wanted to sort of include my precious bb kitty (joplin!) shes been with me through thick and thin, and she surely enjoys sitting on my windowsill and looking at the stars. or, rather, or neighbors houses. i dont think she quite looks at the stars

that being said, im noticing a million mistakes in this upon posting it! however, im tired and would like to play dbd with my bf before going shleepy.
